# data/restaurants.parquet is intentionally NOT gitignored.
# The nixpacks.toml build step downloads it during image build (baked into the
# container), so every container restart reads from the fast local path.
# If the file is present locally you may commit it (it's 142 MB; use git-lfs
# for that), or simply rely on the build step to generate it on Railway.


